    "slug": "log-concavity-tunneling-aqo-convex-functions-spike",
    "excerpt": "A technical briefing on arXiv:2606.23614: lifting the Hamming-weight-with-a-spike AQO tunneling argument onto the structural property of log-concave ground states, with new spectral-gap bounds and a quadratic-ramp extension.",
