    "excerpt": "A briefing on Wang et al.'s (arXiv:2605.29536) study of single-photon scattering in directional waveguide arrays. They reveal how chiral configurations transform spatial coordinates into time-like evolution, mapping to (1+1)D and (2+0)D Dirac equations.",
