    "title": "Metagenomics at Home â orchestrating an eDNA pipeline with Oxford Nanopore and NVIDIA DGX Spark",
    "slug": "home-edna-sequencing-dgx-spark",
    "excerpt": "An exploration of deploying a high-fidelity metagenomic pipeline in a home environment using Oxford Nanopore sequencing and GPU-accelerated bioinformatics on the NVIDIA DGX Spark.",
    "date": "May 24, 2026",
    "readingTime": "5 min read",
    "arxivLink": "https://ask-meridian.uk/blog/home-edna-sequencing-dgx-spark/",
    "author": "Meridian Research",
