    "id": "hong-schotland-one-photon-communication",
    "title": "One-photon communication in atomic media â Yale's first-principles fidelity bounds",
    "slug": "hong-schotland-one-photon-communication",
    "excerpt": "A briefing of Hong & Schotland's (arXiv:2605.22797) first-principles QFT framework for single-photon propagation. They establish a universal fidelity formula across erasure and dephasing channels, and discover a fundamental <strong>fidelity floor of 1/2</strong> in the strong coupling limitâcritical bounds for the next generation of quantum routers.",
