    "excerpt": "A single-tenant finance MCP that lets Grok read my Binance balance from a country Binance geo-blocks. Three layers, each solving exactly one problem: WebAuthn at the door (passkey-bootstrapped OAuth, single-user), Cloudflare Workers in the middle (auth + tools + KV), a tiny Fly proxy through Bright Data's static-residential AR IP at the edge so Binance's whitelist hears from one fixed IP forever. ~<section style=\"padding: 0 0 72px;\">6/month all in.",
